node.text: Tongan athlete Pita Taufatofua is back for the third straight time after first going viral at the 2016 Rio Olympics. node.text: Meghan Trainor is opening up about life as a new mom and her decision to bottle-feed her baby boy. 🙏 Trainor says she initially tried to breastfeed her son Riley but eventually came to the decision that bottle-feeding would be the best route for her and her son. "I was pumping as soon as I got to my room after the C-section. I really struggled making milk. So finally, I was like, 'I'm done!'" Trainor recalls, adding that she "never felt guilty" about her decision to switch to bottle-feeding. ❤️ Tap the bio link for more. | #Regram @meghan_trainor
